    <custom_item>
      type        : RPM_CHECK
      description : "RHEL-09-251010 - RHEL 9 must have the firewalld package installed."
      info        : "\"Firewalld\" provides an easy and effective way to block/limit remote access to the system via ports, services, and protocols.

